---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 215
  - Title: The Book of the Craft of Dying
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Death=The Art of Dying
  - 206
---
Against his will he dieth that hath not learned to die. Learn to die
and thou shalt learn to live, for there shall none learn to live that
hath not learned to die.
